an class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;update&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;Update&lt;/span&gt; apps, or Scoop itself&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;virustotal  Look &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;app&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#x27;s hash &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;on&lt;/span&gt; virustotal.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;which&lt;/span&gt;       Locate a shim/executable (similar to &amp;#x27;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;which&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#x27; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;on&lt;/span&gt; Linux)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;Type&lt;/span&gt; &amp;#x27;scoop &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;help&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;command&amp;gt;&amp;#x27; to get &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;help&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; a specific command.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
